::Annihilator::

Annihilator jumps out of his chair, a missle launcher in his hand. "Wait!" he 
yells at Unitron. He knew there no possible way for him to defeat this bot, 
so he simply wouldn't.

"We can team up. Using this ship as our base of operations, we'd be 
unstoppable!" he waits for Unitron to answer, still holding the missile 
launcher aimed at the other bot.
